equipment_1.name: Surgical Cap
equipment_1.description:
The Surgical Cap is a crucial item in the medical and healthcare field, designed to maintain cleanliness and prevent contamination in sterile environments. 
 Crafted from high-quality, breathable materials, this cap is essential for both healthcare professionals and patients during surgical and clinical procedures.
